      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Al Husayn Bin Muhammad, from Muhammad Bin Ahmad Al Nahdy, from Mus’ab Bin Yazeed, from Al Awwan Bin al Zubeyr, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘The one who softens his face would soften his knowledge’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "3. Al-Husayn ibn Muhammad has narrated from Muhammad ibn Ahmad al-Nahdi from Mus’ab ibn Yazid from al -‘Awwam ibn al-Zubayr from abu ‘Abd Allah (a.s.) who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah (a.s.) has said, ‘One whose face is thin (bashful and shy) has thin knowledge.’” "
        ]
      }
